These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: thai, spanish, british, indian
Food: orange, banana, pineapple, onion
1. Food:onion is on the left of Nationality:british##1
2. Nationality:thai is on the left of Food:banana##1
3. Nationality:indian is in an odd position##4
4. Food:pineapple is on the left or right of Food:onion##3
5. Nationality:thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | thai | spanish | indian | british |
| Food        | orange | banana   | onion | pineapple    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Music-Genre: punk, country, reggae, folk
Pet: goldfish, ferret, hedgehog, lizard
1. Music-Genre:country is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1
2. Pet:goldfish is on the left of Pet:hedgehog##1
3. Pet:hedgehog is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:goldfish == Music-Genre:punk##1
5. Pet:ferret is on the right of Pet:hedgehog##1
6. Pet:goldfish == Music-Genre:punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | punk  | country  | folk |
| Pet   | lizard    | goldfish | hedgehog | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Color: ivory, brown, orange, ebony
Job: accountant, entrepreneur, analyst, freelancer
1. Color:ebony is on the left or right of Job:freelancer##3
2. Color:orange is in an even position##4
3. Job:freelancer is on the left or right of Color:brown##3
4. Job:freelancer is on the right of Job:analyst##1
5. Job:accountant is in an odd position##4
6. Color:brown is on the right of Color:orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color          | ebony | orange | brown    | ivory      |
| Job   | analyst        | freelancer     | accountant | entrepreneur |

