.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Pet: frog, pony, horse, dog
Transport: skateboard, helicopter, boat, motorbike
1. Pet:pony is between Transport:skateboard and Transport:motorbike##2
2. Pet:dog is on the left of Pet:frog##1
3. Transport:boat is in an odd position##4
4. Transport:helicopter is on the left of Transport:motorbike##1
5. Transport:helicopter is on the right of Pet:frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet         | dog | frog | pony | horse |
| Transport   | boat       | skateboard   | helicopter    | motorbike  |

