2. Movie-Genre:crime == Pet:cat##1
3. Movie-Genre:family is on the right of Pet:bird##1
4. Pet:mouse is on the far left##1
5. Pet:pony is in an odd position##4
6. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | mouse  | bird    | pony   | cat       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | mystery | family | crime |

