.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
City: hannover, marseilles, san-francisco, miami
Music-Genre: rock, techno, gospel, disco
1. Music-Genre:disco is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:gospel is on the left of Music-Genre:rock##1
3. City:miami is on the left of City:san-francisco##1
4. Music-Genre:disco == City:hannover##1
5. City:miami is on the left or right of Music-Genre:rock##3
6. Music-Genre:techno is on the right of Music-Genre:rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| City   | hannover | miami | san-francisco | marseilles    |
| Music-Genre     | disco | gospel  | rock     | techno |

