2. Transport:snowmobile is on the right of Color:fuchsia##1
3. Transport:boat is between Transport:snowmobile and Color:amber##2
4. Color:fuchsia is in an odd position##4
5. Transport:boat is on the left or right of Transport:snowmobile##3
6. Color:light-blue is on the left or right of Transport:bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | light-blue       | amber   | fuchsia | apricot |
| Transport   | trike | bus | boat        | snowmobile    |

