2. Game:bridge is on the left or right of Game:billiard##3
3. Game:scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
4. City:hamburg is on the left of City:liverpool##1
5. City:liverpool is on the right of Game:billiard##1
6. City:hamburg is in an even position##4
7. City:rome == Game:canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Game   | scrabble | billiard    | bridge       | canasta |
| City       | colone  | hamburg | liverpool | rome  |

