2. Birthday:january is on the left or right of Nationality:spanish##3
3. Nationality:brazilian is between Birthday:november and Nationality:spanish##2
4. Birthday:january is on the far left or far right##3
5. Nationality:american is on the right of Birthday:february##1
6. Nationality:american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Birthday         | november | august   | february | january |
| Nationality   | canadian          | brazilian | spanish         | american  |

 